name: Growmore Enterprises
overview:
Established in year 2012, we, “Growmore Enterprises”, are among the distinguished organizations engaged in importing and exporting Maize, Sorghum, Millet and other Food Products. The range offered by us comprises Maize, Sorghum, Millet, Garlic, Dorb, Salt, Safflower, Wheat, Rice, Tamarind, Turmeric Power and Chick Peas Barley.

Our Team: Experienced professionals Quality controllers Sales And marketing executives Administrators

Quality Assurance: Since the vary first day of our inception, we are giving utmost priority to the quality standard of the products offered by us. We ensure that the products offered by us comply with industry laid guidelines and using and optimum quality material to manufacture these products.

Our Quality Standards: Being a quality conscious, we make sure to deliver high quality animal feeding products and raw materials, which are safe & hygienic for animals and cattle. We are totally committed to meet and exceed the expectation of our clients by providing them finest quality products as well as services. We as a team also adhere to stringent product quality standards, and test the products at various parameters before dispatching them. We strive hard to sustain the quality in our range of products.

The Future: All the companies believe in long-term relationships where mutual trust is the key. They are therefore consciously working on strengthening, the relationship with the existing clients and exploring new markets with a renewed interest and zeal.
